name: Druid's forest
description:
The ancient forest, haunted with all sorts of spirits, living on the edge of cold world. The place where not many people are dare to walk in..  where every living soul lost his mind if he's not strong enough...  and after that, all those poor souls staying to live as a tree, besides all the others. Terifide, sad, crying for freedome, BUT always ready to help the strong ones.

That work was made in 2018y.
